stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> SellerLoggedIn: Seller accesses platform

    SellerLoggedIn --> FillPropertyForm: Clicks "Add Property"
    FillPropertyForm --> SelectMedia: Fills type, area, rooms, price, location, description

    SelectMedia --> SubmitForm: Selects images/media files
    SubmitForm --> BackendValidation: POST /api/properties

    state ValidationResult <<choice>>
    BackendValidation --> ValidationResult

    ValidationResult --> ShowErrors: Validation fails
    ShowErrors --> FillPropertyForm: User corrects input

    ValidationResult --> CreateRecord: Validation passes
    CreateRecord --> GeneratePresignedURLs: Property saved in DB (pending_media=true)
    GeneratePresignedURLs --> ReturnURLs: S3 presigned URLs generated

    ReturnURLs --> DirectUpload: Frontend receives URLs
    DirectUpload --> UploadToS3: PUT files directly to S3

    state UploadResult <<choice>>
    UploadToS3 --> UploadResult

    UploadResult --> ConfirmUpload: Upload successful
    UploadResult --> RetryUpload: Upload failed
    RetryUpload --> DirectUpload: Retry

    ConfirmUpload --> UpdateDB: PUT /api/properties/:id/media
    UpdateDB --> PropertyActive: pending_media = false, uploaded_at set

    PropertyActive --> [*]: Property visible in search results
